# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Plan / design docs location policy
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Store project plans in the top-level `plans/` folder.
# Ignore plan-like markdown elsewhere to avoid scattered docs.
**/*PLAN*.md
**/*.plan.md
!plans/
!plans/**
